  <brief_title>Impact of Preoperative Chemotherapy on Complications and Regeneration After Resection of Colorectal Liver Metastases</brief_title>
  <official_title>Impact of Preoperative Chemotherapy on Complications and Regeneration After Resection of Colorectal Liver Metastases</official_title>
